<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Julia Jacobson | The Photographer</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container header-inner">
            <div class="logo">
                Julia Jacobson
                <span>The Photographer</span>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Works</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Instagram</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="column-2 about-img">
                    <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/9e/49/4d/9e494d4c73755d108a32dd747b939d81.jpg" alt="Julia Jacobson">
                </div>
                <div class="column-2 about-text">
                    <h3>My name is Julia Jacobson</h3>
                    <p>I am a professional photographer based in New York. I specialize in portrait, landscape, and event photography. My goal is to capture the beauty of the moment and tell your story through images.</p>
                    <p>I have been shooting for over 10 years and have worked with clients from all over the world.</p>
                    
                    <div class="contact-info">
                        123 Main Street<br>
                        New York, NY 10001<br>
                        +1 (555) 123-4567<br>
                        julia@jacobson.com<br>
                        www.juliajacobson.com
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="works">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">My Last Works</h2>
            <div class="gallery-grid">
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="https://technovybor.ru/wa-data/public/shop/products/00/webp/94/39/3994/images/6018/6018.520.webp" alt="Camera">
                    <div class="gallery-overlay">
                        <p>Camera Gear</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5b9fbb28ee1759803459c790/1537298542319-QDOCNRWUXMSTELRILL8C/beautiful-natural-light-portraits-by-toronto-photographer-livepixels.jpg" alt="Portrait">
                    <div class="gallery-overlay">
                        <p>Portrait Session</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/76/A_Wedding_Story.jpg/250px-A_Wedding_Story.jpg" alt="Wedding">
                    <div class="gallery-overlay">
                        <p>Wedding Story</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516961642265-531546e84af2?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Film">
                    <div class="gallery-overlay">
                        <p>Film Photography</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500634245200-e5245c7574ef?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Landscape">
                    <div class="gallery-overlay">
                        <p>Nature Landscape</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTu2gQ7ZLr97kqLJiM_3fK7V0LBHDLm7qcLrw&s" alt="Fashion">
                    <div class="gallery-overlay">
                        <p>Fashion Shoot</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="blog">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="blog-item">
                <div class="blog-img">
                    <img src="https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/none-335643419.jpg" alt="Coffee">
                </div>
                <div class="blog-content">
                    <h3>Morning coffee</h3>
                    <p>Coffee lovers everywhere can't get enough morning coffee!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="blog-item">
                <div class="blog-img">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513519245088-0e12902e5a38?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Interior">
                </div>
                <div class="blog-content">
                    <h3>Interior Details</h3>
                    <p>Sometimes the smallest details tell the biggest stories. Capturing the texture of old wood and the play of shadows in this vintage apartment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="large-photo-section">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Landscape">
        <div class="photo-caption">
            <h3>Landscape Photo</h3>
            <p>Amazing natural light and composition make this photo stand out.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-social">
                <a href="#">Follow me on Instagram</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-social">
                <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#">Twitter</a>
                <a href="#">Pinterest</a>
                <a href="#">500px</a>
            </div>
            <p class="copyright">&copy; Copyright 2023 Julia Jacobson</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
